---
title: "RAG Pipeline — State Machine"
---
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> ExtractQuery: Receive OpenAI-format messages

    ExtractQuery: Extract Last User Message
    note right of ExtractQuery
        Only the last "user" message is used.
        Previous turns discarded (stateless Phase 1).
    end note

    ExtractQuery --> InputGuard: user_query extracted

    InputGuard: Input Guard Check
    note right of InputGuard
        POST /classify
        role: "input"
        timeout: GUARD_TIMEOUT_S (10s)
    end note

    InputGuard --> ReturnApology: UNSAFE
    InputGuard --> GuardUnreachable: Service Error
    InputGuard --> EmbedQuery: SAFE

    GuardUnreachable: Guard Unreachable
    note right of GuardUnreachable
        Fail closed — treat as unsafe
    end note
    GuardUnreachable --> ReturnApology

    EmbedQuery: Embed Query (Dense Vector)
    note right of EmbedQuery
        Qwen3-Embedding-0.6B
        prompt_name="query"
        1024 dimensions
    end note

    EmbedQuery --> HybridRetrieve

    HybridRetrieve: Hybrid Retrieval from Qdrant
    note right of HybridRetrieve
        Dense: top-40 prefetch
        Sparse (BM25): top-40 prefetch
        RRF fusion (k=60) → top-20
    end note

    HybridRetrieve --> Rerank: top-20 candidates

    Rerank: Rerank Candidates
    note right of Rerank
        Qwen3-Reranker-0.6B
        yes/no logit scoring
        Select top RERANK_TOP_N (5)
    end note

    Rerank --> EvalFallback: reranked chunks + scores

    EvalFallback: Evaluate Web Fallback Trigger

    state eval_check <<choice>>
    EvalFallback --> eval_check

    eval_check --> WebFallback: chunk_count < 3\nOR top_score < 0.5
    eval_check --> CheckEmpty: Both conditions pass

    WebFallback: Tavily Web Search
    note right of WebFallback
        TavilyClient.search()
        max_results: TAVILY_MAX_RESULTS (5)
        Merge: Qdrant chunks first, then web results
        Tag web results: source_type="web"
    end note

    WebFallback --> CheckEmpty: merged context
    WebFallback --> CheckEmpty: Tavily error → use existing chunks

    CheckEmpty: Check Combined Context

    state empty_check <<choice>>
    CheckEmpty --> empty_check

    empty_check --> ReturnNoContext: context is empty
    empty_check --> BuildPrompt: context has chunks

    ReturnNoContext: Return "No Context" Message
    note right of ReturnNoContext
        "Xin lỗi, tôi không thể tìm thấy
        thông tin liên quan."
        Skip LLM call entirely.
    end note
    ReturnNoContext --> [*]

    BuildPrompt: Build RAG Prompt
    note right of BuildPrompt
        System: Vietnamese economics expert prompt
        User: Context chunks [1]..[N] + user query
        Chunks ordered by reranker score (highest first)
    end note

    BuildPrompt --> GenerateAnswer

    GenerateAnswer: LLM Generation
    note right of GenerateAnswer
        Qwen3.5-4B via vLLM
        enable_thinking: False
        timeout: LLM_TIMEOUT_S (60s)
    end note

    GenerateAnswer --> OutputGuard: draft answer

    OutputGuard: Output Guard Check
    note right of OutputGuard
        POST /classify
        role: "output"
        prompt: original user query
    end note

    OutputGuard --> AppendCitations: SAFE
    OutputGuard --> RetryGeneration: UNSAFE (1st time)

    RetryGeneration: Retry with Safety Feedback
    note right of RetryGeneration
        Append safety feedback to prompt:
        "Câu trả lời trước đó bị đánh giá
        là không an toàn..."
        Generate new answer via LLM
    end note

    RetryGeneration --> OutputGuard2: retried answer

    OutputGuard2: Re-check Output Guard

    OutputGuard2 --> AppendCitations: SAFE
    OutputGuard2 --> ReturnApology: STILL UNSAFE

    AppendCitations: Append Citation Block
    note right of AppendCitations
        ---
        Nguồn tham khảo:
        [1] title — source, date — url
        [2] ...
    end note

    AppendCitations --> SimulateStream

    SimulateStream: Simulate SSE Streaming
    note right of SimulateStream
        Split on whitespace
        Yield each word as SSE chunk
        ~15ms inter-chunk delay
        Citations as final chunk
    end note

    SimulateStream --> [*]

    ReturnApology: Return Apology Message
    note right of ReturnApology
        APOLOGY_MESSAGE env var
        "Xin loi, toi khong the tra loi
        cau hoi nay."
    end note
    ReturnApology --> [*]
